# Project Structure

- All source code goes in `src/`. Entry point is `src/main.py`.
- All tests go in `tests/`. Mirror the `src/` structure (e.g., `tests/test_main.py`).
- Model artifacts go in `models/` with naming: `{model_type}_{dataset}_{YYYYMMDD}.joblib`.
- Config via environment variables or `.env` file. No hardcoded paths.
- No single-file applications. Separate concerns: `src/main.py` (app), `src/model.py` (model loading/training), `src/schemas.py` (pydantic models), `src/config.py` (settings).
